  "texts": [
    "Examples of tasks include sentiment analysis, toxicity detection, text classification, and summarization.",
    "The category includes data (i.e., post text and image) produced directly by individuals (first-party), as well as data collected about the individual or their user behavior (third-party).",
    "Financial News & Media.",
    "Produced by major news agencies, news about current events and finance informs markets about macroeconomics, company earnings, and opinionated analysis.",
    "News types range from real-time reports and market analyses to press releases."
